sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTPSrv as HTTP Server (FastAPI)<br/>8080/TCP Optional TLS
    participant GRPCSrv as gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP Optional TLS
    participant PredictSvc as GlobalPredictServicer
    participant TrainSvc as GlobalTrainServicer
    participant ModelMgr as ModelManager
    participant Module as ModuleBase.run()
    participant MMesh as ModelMesh Controller
    participant MRSvc as ModelRuntimeServicer
    participant FS as Filesystem<br/>(Model Storage)
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>4317/4318/TCP

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 1: Model Inference (gRPC)
    Client->>GRPCSrv: gRPC Predict RPC<br/>8085/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    GRPCSrv->>PredictSvc: Route to servicer
    PredictSvc->>ModelMgr: retrieve_model(model_id)
    ModelMgr->>Module: module.run(input)
    Module-->>ModelMgr: Prediction result
    ModelMgr-->>PredictSvc: DataBase response
    PredictSvc-->>GRPCSrv: Protobuf response
    GRPCSrv-->>Client: gRPC Response
    GRPCSrv->>OTel: Export trace span<br/>OTLP gRPC/HTTP

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 2: Model Inference (HTTP REST)
    Client->>HTTPSrv: POST /api/v1/{task}/predict<br/>8080/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    HTTPSrv->>PredictSvc: Translate HTTP → servicer call
    PredictSvc->>ModelMgr: retrieve_model(model_id)
    ModelMgr->>Module: module.run(input)
    Module-->>ModelMgr: Prediction result
    ModelMgr-->>PredictSvc: DataBase response
    PredictSvc-->>HTTPSrv: JSON / SSE stream
    HTTPSrv-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON (or SSE stream)

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 3: ModelMesh Model Loading
    MMesh->>MRSvc: loadModel(model_id, path)<br/>Unix socket /tmp/mmesh/grpc.sock
    MRSvc->>ModelMgr: load_model(model_id, path)
    ModelMgr->>FS: Read model artifacts<br/>File I/O
    FS-->>ModelMgr: Model files
    ModelMgr-->>MRSvc: LoadModelResponse (size)
    MRSvc-->>MMesh: Model loaded (size bytes)

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 4: Training Job
    Client->>GRPCSrv: Training RPC<br/>8085/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    GRPCSrv->>TrainSvc: Route to servicer
    TrainSvc->>ModelMgr: train(module_class, train_params)
    ModelMgr->>Module: LocalModelTrainer<br/>DestroyableThread/Process
    Note right of Module: Async training<br/>in background thread
    Module->>FS: Save trained model<br/>File I/O
    TrainSvc-->>GRPCSrv: TrainingJob ID
    GRPCSrv-->>Client: Training started

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 5: Health Check
    Client->>HTTPSrv: GET /health<br/>8080/TCP
    HTTPSrv-->>Client: 200 OK
    Client->>GRPCSrv: grpc.health.v1.Health.Check<br/>8085/TCP
    GRPCSrv-->>Client: SERVING
